---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Systems — Efe Ertugrul"
	description="Industry systems case studies: context, constraints, architecture decisions, tradeoffs, outcomes."
	activeNav="systems"
>
	<h1>Systems</h1>
	<p>Case studies, not projects.</p>

	<section class="grid">
		<article class="card">
			<h2>Simmunome — AI bioinformatics platform</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Context:</strong> multi-service platform for compute-heavy scientific workflows.</li>
				<li><strong>Constraints:</strong> cost, reliability, large datasets, research velocity.</li>
				<li><strong>Architecture:</strong> Kubernetes microservices, secure pipelines, CI/CD + observability.</li>
				<li><strong>Outcomes:</strong> production deployments that unblock R&amp;D and daily operations.</li>
				<li><strong>What I’d change:</strong> tighten service boundaries and harden failure modes further.</li>
			</ul>
		</article>

		<article class="card">
			<h2>Infra-heavy system — compute orchestration</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Context:</strong> recurring compute jobs with bursty demand and long runtimes.</li>
				<li><strong>Constraints:</strong> queueing, retries, idempotency, cost ceilings.</li>
				<li><strong>Architecture:</strong> workload isolation, autoscaling, structured telemetry.</li>
				<li><strong>Tradeoffs:</strong> fewer moving parts over maximal flexibility.</li>
			</ul>
		</article>

		<article class="card">
			<h2>Regulated system — banking services (TEB / BNP Paribas)</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Context:</strong> core banking features under strict release cycles.</li>
				<li><strong>Constraints:</strong> compliance, ACID guarantees, security, auditability.</li>
				<li><strong>Architecture:</strong> Spring Boot services, RBAC, monitoring, tests.</li>
				<li><strong>Outcomes:</strong> secure, reliable workflows for transactions and account operations.</li>
			</ul>
		</article>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 14px;
		margin-top: 18px;
	}

	.card {
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: 16px;
		padding: 14px 14px;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
	}

	.card h2 {
		margin-top: 0;
	}

	:global(strong) {
		color: var(--text);
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	@media (max-width: 960px) {
		.grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>


